</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>數碼港電競嘉年華活動　爆汗運動電競 ＋ 競速無人機大賽</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/10/delf-2021-event/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=delf-2021-event</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tang Renee]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 10 Dec 2021 06:51:07 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[玩樂好去處]]></category><category><![CDATA[2021]]></category><category><![CDATA[delf]]></category><category><![CDATA[數碼娛樂領袖論壇]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1075307</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近年在疫情下數碼娛樂漸趨流行，遊戲與電競等新興數碼產業不斷有突破及新原素加入。數碼娛樂領袖論壇（DELF）今年 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近年在疫情下數碼娛樂漸趨流行，遊戲與電競等新興數碼產業不斷有突破及新原素加入。數碼娛樂領袖論壇（DELF）今年再度舉辦，於 12 月 10 至 12 號一連三日在數碼港舉行多項科技相關的論壇及電競嘉年華活動，相當適合一家大細、業內人士、及各科技愛好者。</p><h2>5 大數碼娛樂體驗區，玩家可親身挑戰</h2><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1075308 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/unnamed-1.jpg" alt="" width="512" height="287" /> ▲今年的活動場地相當大，當中劃分了 3 大主要區域，有戶內有戶外，足夠玩上大半日時間</p><h2>水底機械人＋競速無人機  玩勻「海陸空」場地</h2><p>由香港城市大學主理的水底機械人工作坊，參加者可嘗試操控及製作水底機械人，更可體驗一下嶄新的水底足球對決。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075309 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC04102-694x432.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="432" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC04102-694x432.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC04102-1280x796.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC04102-768x478.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC04102-1536x956.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC04102-2048x1274.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC04102-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>喜歡 VR 電競的朋友不能錯過 SWIFT² 智能運動衣，它透過 NMES 科技能製造出即時觸覺反饋，結合 VR 遊戲，可為玩家帶來身歷其境的體驗。現場有玩家表示，玩槍 game 時彷似有子彈穿過皮膚的感覺，相當過癮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075310 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03045-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03045-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03045-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03045.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而《2021 FAI 香港競速無人機公開賽》（FAI World Drone Racing Championships）是首次香港的專業競速無人機賽事，大型戶外場地內設有觀眾席讓大家感受當中的極速快感。部分賽事更會在入夜後舉行，無人機將配以燈光效果更為特別。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075312 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03091-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03091-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03091-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03091.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075311 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03087-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03087-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03087-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03087.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>必玩爆汗「體育科技」主題區域 6 大項目</h2><p>六大項目包括：賽車、足球、高爾夫球、射擊、划艇及單車，當中划艇及單車最具挑戰性，玩完真的像做完真正運動一樣，出到一身汗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075316 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03164-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03164-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03164-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03164.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075315 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03172-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03172-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03172-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03172.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075317 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03148-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03148-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03148-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03148.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075314 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03152-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03152-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03152-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03152.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲體力充沛的朋友不妨全部 6 項運動都挑戰一下</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075313 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03137-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03137-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03137-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03137.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> ▲ VR 射擊遊戲可以組隊和多位朋友對戰</p><h2>糅合科技與藝術 「無限光子」互動投影</h2><p>參加者可以置身在浮燈叠影的效果中跳舞和互動，七彩繽紛的光影會隨著您的身體擺動懸浮出來，「打卡」一流。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075318 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03030-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03030-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03030-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/DSC03030.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>業界焦點論壇  邀請 70 多位全球星級講者</h2><p>解構多個熱門話題，包括元宇宙、區塊鏈遊戲、NFT 技術應用等；亦有探討商業模式及價值鏈如何超越現狀。大會共邀請到全球超過 70 位星級演講嘉賓，當中不容錯過的焦點講者包括：</p><ul><li>前華特迪士尼、華納兄弟以及夢工場動畫製作人和工作室總裁；浸大電影學院傑出訪問學人 Max Howard 霍文東博士</li><li>UM 美國創新部主管; IPG Media Lab 策略部高級副總裁 Adam Simon 先生</li><li>Meta 遊戲行業大中華區總監趙倩女士</li><li>Naffiti 聯合創辦人陳奐仁先生</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1075319 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/guest.png" alt="" width="1009" height="323" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/guest.png 1009w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/guest-694x222.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/guest-768x246.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>其他節目：</p><ul><li>Talon Esports 粉絲見面會 (12 月 11 日）</li><li>2021 環太平洋大學聯盟（APRU）電競 MetaGame 會議、人才分組論壇 (12 月 11 日）09:30-18:00</li><li>哈利波特：魔法醒覺 Yesports 最強巫師對決 (亞洲盃) 決賽 (12 月 12 日）09:00-18:00</li></ul><p><strong><u>活動詳情：</u></strong></p><p>2021 數碼娛樂領袖論壇 (DELF)</p><p>地點：數碼港商場</p><p>日期：10 – 12 Dec （星期五 – 日）</p><p>更多活動詳情：<span role="gridcell"><a class="oajrlxb2 g5ia77u1 qu0x051f esr5mh6w e9989ue4 r7d6kgcz rq0escxv nhd2j8a9 nc684nl6 p7hjln8o kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x jb